plot: Prospero gains renewed magic that creates havoc with the world's technology. Flynn and Baird must travel back to 1611 to battle Prospero and thwart his scheme to recreate a forest utopia.

When Prospero casts a spell that changes the world into a forest utopia, the Librarians must find a way to stop him. And they realize that a note they received earlier during their encounter with Prospero was written by Flynn in 1611. So he decides to go back in time with Eve, But as they leave something happens to the device they used to go back in time. So Jenkins and the others try to find another way from to return. When they arrive in 1611 Flynn and Eve meet Shakespeare and try to get him to help them with Prospero,—rcs0411@yahoo.com
